  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Determine the objective response rate (ORR = CR + PR) to a regimen of SDX-105 plus rituximab in patients with relapsed indolent or mantle cell non-Hodgkin's lymphoma</measure>
    <time_frame>4-6 months</time_frame>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>• To characterize the safety profile of SDX-105 plus rituximab in this patient population • To determine the one-year and Kaplan-Meier estimates of progression-free survival (PFS) rates • To determine the median duration of response (DR)</measure>
    <time_frame>4-6 months</time_frame>
  </secondary_outcome>
